de.png","info_text":"<p>你以难以置信的速度闪现至附近 10 码的一个目标身边并造成 <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">1%, 1%, 1%, 1%, 2%<\/acronym> 伤害。<\/p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"主动技能","name":"闪电突袭","points":5,"random_ego":"attack","range":"10.0","requires_target":true,"short_name":"KEEPSAKE_BLINDSIDE","source_code":["data\/talents\/misc\/npcs.lua",2179],"type":["undead\/keepsake",1],"use_speed":"武器"}],"type":"undead\/keepsake"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"undead","description":" 食尸鬼的天赋。","generic":true,"name":"食尸鬼","points":1,"talents":[{"generic":true,"id":"T_GHOUL","image":"ghoul.png","info_text":"<p>增强食尸鬼的身体，增加 <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">4, 8, 12, 16, 20<\/acronym> 点力量和体质。<\/p><p>你的身体对伤害抗性极高，任何一次伤害不会让你失去超过 50% 最大生命。<\/p>","mode":"被动技能","multi_require":true,"name":"食尸鬼","points":5,"range":"近战\/单体","require":["等级 0","等级 1","等级 2","等级 3","等级 4"],"short_name":"GHOUL","source_code":["data\/talents\/undeads\/ghoul.lua",20],"type":["undead\/ghoul",1],"use_speed":"标准"},{"cooldown":"<acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">18, 14, 11, 10, 9<\/acronym>","direct_hit":true,"fixed_cooldown":true,"generic":true,"id":"T_GHOULISH_LEAP","image":"ghoulish_leap.png","info_text":"<p>跳向你的目标。<\/p><p>落地后你的整体速度增加 <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">20%, 25%, 27%, 29%, 31%<\/acronym> ，持续 4 回合。<\/p>","mode":"主动技能","multi_require":true,"name":"定向跳跃","points":5,"range":"<acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">5.0, 7.0, 8.0, 10.0, 11.0<\/acronym>","require":["等级 4","等级 5","等级 6","等级 7","等级 8"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"GHOULISH_LEAP","source_code":["data\/talents\/undeads\/ghoul.lua",40],"type":["undead\/ghoul",2],"use_speed":"标准"},{"cooldown":20,"generic":true,"id":"T_RETCH","image":"retch.png","info_text":"<p>向你周围的空地上呕吐，治疗任何在这空地上的不死族并伤害敌方单位。 <\/p><p>持续 10 回合并造成 <acronym class=\"variable\" t