, 16, 20<\/acronym> 点力量和敏捷。<\/p>","mode":"被动技能","multi_require":true,"name":"骷髅","points":5,"range":"近战\/单体","require":["等级 0","等级 1","等级 2","等级 3","等级 4"],"short_name":"SKELETON","source_code":["data\/talents\/undeads\/skeleton.lua",20],"type":["undead\/skeleton",1],"use_speed":"标准"},{"cooldown":"<acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">24, 20, 17, 16, 15<\/acronym>","generic":true,"id":"T_BONE_ARMOUR","image":"bone_armour.png","info_text":"<p>在你的周围制造一个能吸收 <acronym class=\"variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30,<br>敏捷 100\">511, 634, 727, 804, 871<\/acronym> 点伤害的骨盾。持续 10 回合。 <\/p><p>护盾的最大吸收值受敏捷值加成。<\/p>","mode":"主动技能","multi_require":true,"name":"骨质盔甲","points":5,"range":"近战\/单体","require":["等级 4","等级 5","等级 6","等级 7","等级 8"],"short_name":"BONE_ARMOUR","source_code":["data\/talents\/undeads\/skeleton.lua",37],"type":["undead\/skeleton",2],"use_speed":"标准"},{"generic":true,"id":"T_RESILIENT_BONES","image":"resilient_bones.png","info_text":"<p>你的骨头充满弹性，至多减少 <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">12%, 25%, 33%, 40%, 45%<\/acronym> 所有负面状态持续的时间。<\/p>","mode":"被动技能","multi_require":true,"name":"弹力骨骼","points":5,"range":"近战\/单体","require":["等级 8","等级 9","等级 10","等级 11","等级 12"],"short_name":"RESILIENT_BONES","source_code":["data\/talents\/undeads\/skeleton.lua",61],"type":["undead\/skeleton",3],"use_speed":"标准"},{"cooldown":"<acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">29, 21, 18, 16, 15<\/acronym>","generic":true,"id":"T_SKELETON_REASSEMBLE","image":"skeleton_reassemble.png","info_text":"<p>重新组合你的骨头，治疗你 <acronym class=\"talent-variable\" title=\"以下状况的数值<br>技能等级 1-5,<br>技能系数 1.30\">159, 328, 456, 562, 655<\/acronym> 点生命值。 <\/p><p>在等级 5 时你将会得到重塑自我的能力，被摧毁后可以原地满血复活。（仅限 1 次）<\/p>","is_heal":true,"mode":"主动技能","multi_require":true,"name":"重组","no_unlearn_last":true,"points":5,"range":"近战\/单体","require":["等级 12","等级 13","等级 14","等级 15","等级 16"],"short_na